<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Wynn Tax Solutions</title>
    <style>
      body,
      table,
      td,
      p,
      a {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      body {
        background-color: #f4f6f9;
        font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      img {
        border: 0;
        display: block;
        outline: none;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .email-wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #f4f6f9;
        padding: 30px 0;
      }
      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }
      .email-header {
        background-color: #1a2744;
        padding: 30px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .email-header img {
        max-width: 200px;
        height: auto;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .hero-banner {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2744 0%, #2c4a7c 100%);
        padding: 28px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .hero-banner h1 {
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.3;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .hero-banner p {
        color: #b8c9e0;
        font-size: 15px;
        margin-top: 8px;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 36px 40px;
        color: #333333;
      }
      .email-body p {
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: #444444;
      }
      .greeting {
        font-size: 17px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1a2744;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .highlight-box {
        background-color: #f0f5fb;
        border-left: 4px solid #2c4a7c;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 20px 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }
      .highlight-box p {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .highlight-box p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
      .highlight-box strong {
        color: #1a2744;
      }
      .cta-wrapper {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 28px 0;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #2c4a7c;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 14px 36px;
        border-radius: 6px;
      }
      .divider {
        border: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #e8ecf1;
        margin: 28px 0;
      }
      .step-item {
        margin-bottom: 14px;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #444;
      }
      .email-footer {
        background-color: #1a2744;
        padding: 28px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .email-footer p {
        color: #8fa3bf;
        font-size: 12px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      .email-footer a {
        color: #b8c9e0;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      .footer-phone {
        font-size: 16px !important;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        margin-bottom: 12px !important;
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 620px) {
        .email-body,
        .email-header,
        .hero-banner,
        .email-footer {
          padding-left: 24px !important;
          padding-right: 24px !important;
        }
        .hero-banner h1 {
          font-size: 20px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <table
        class="email-container"
        role="presentation"
        cellpadding="0"
        cellspacing="0"
        width="100%"
      >

        <!-- Header / Logo -->
        <tr>
          <td class="email-header">
            <img src="cid:emailLogo" alt="Wynn Tax Solutions" />
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Hero Banner -->
        <tr>
          <td class="hero-banner">
            <h1>Welcome to Wynn Tax Solutions</h1>
            <p>Your partner in tax relief &amp; resolution</p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Body Content -->
        <tr>
          <td class="email-body">

            <p class="greeting">Hi {{name}},</p>

            <p>
              Thank you for reaching out! We're glad you connected with us. At
              Wynn Tax Solutions, we specialize in helping individuals and
              businesses resolve tax issues with the IRS and state agencies
              &mdash; so you can get back to what matters most.
            </p>

            <div class="highlight-box">
              <p><strong>How we help our clients:</strong></p>
              <p>&#10003; IRS &amp; state tax debt resolution</p>
              <p>&#10003; Offers in Compromise &amp; payment plans</p>
              <p>&#10003; Unfiled tax returns &amp; compliance</p>
              <p>&#10003; Levy, lien &amp; garnishment relief</p>
              <p>&#10003; Audit representation &amp; defense</p>
              <p>&#10003; Penalty abatement &amp; interest reduction</p>
            </div>

            <p>
              We've attached our
              <strong>Tax Solutions Guide</strong>
              to this email &mdash; it walks you through our process, what to
              expect, and how we've helped thousands of clients reduce or
              resolve their tax burdens.
            </p>

            <hr class="divider" />

            <p
              style="font-weight:600; color:#1a2744; font-size:16px; margin-bottom:16px;"
            >
              What happens next?
            </p>

            <div class="step-item">
              &#128203;
              <strong>Review your guide</strong>
              &mdash; Learn about our services and how we approach your case.
            </div>
            <div class="step-item">
              &#128222;
              <strong>Expect a call</strong>
              &mdash; A Wynn Tax consultant will reach out to discuss your
              situation.
            </div>
            <div class="step-item">
              &#128737;
              <strong>Get protected</strong>
              &mdash; We'll outline a strategy tailored to your tax situation.
            </div>

            <p>
              Don't want to wait? Schedule your free consultation now or call us
              directly.
            </p>

            <div class="cta-wrapper">
              <a href="{{scheduleUrl}}" class="cta-button">Schedule Your Free
                Consultation</a>
            </div>

            <p style="text-align:center; font-size:14px; color:#666;">
              Or call us toll-free:
              <strong style="color:#1a2744;">866-770-3749</strong>
            </p>

            <hr class="divider" />

            <p style="font-size:13px; color:#888; line-height:1.6;">
              You're receiving this email because you expressed interest through
              one of our advertising partners. If you believe this was sent in
              error, please disregard this message or reply to let us know.
            </p>

          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <tr>
          <td class="email-footer">
            <p class="footer-phone">&#128222; 866-770-3749</p>
            <p><strong style="color:#fff;">Wynn Tax Solutions</strong></p>
            <p>Tax Resolution &amp; Relief Services</p>
            <p style="margin-top:10px;">
              <a
                href="https://www.wynntaxsolutions.com"
              >wynntaxsolutions.com</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top:14px; font-size:11px; color:#6b829e;">
              &copy;
              {{year}}
              Wynn Tax Solutions. All rights reserved.
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>

      </table>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>